Create a 30-second avatar-less marketing advertisement for Inovio Tech.
Do NOT use any AI avatar or talking head.
This is a voiceover-only video using motion graphics, B-roll, typography, and logos.

FULL SCRIPT (voiceover only):

“At Inovio Tech, innovation isn’t just a buzzword—it’s how we work.
We help businesses turn complex ideas into smart, scalable technology.
From strategy to execution, our solutions are built for speed, performance, and growth.
Trusted by partners shaping the digital world.
We don’t just deliver technology—we deliver results.
Inovio Tech. Building the future of digital solutions.”

SCENE STRUCTURE:

Scene 1 – Hook (0–4s):
Dark-to-light transition.
Abstract tech animation with flowing lines and digital grids.
On-screen text (animated):
“Innovation that works.”

Scene 2 – Problem to Solution (4–9s):
B-roll visuals: modern offices, teams collaborating, developers working, UI dashboards.
Subtle motion graphic overlays.
On-screen text:
“Turning complex ideas into smart technology”

Scene 3 – Core Value (9–14s):
Clean, modern transitions.
B-roll: cloud infrastructure, code visuals, system architecture graphics.
Text highlights appear sequentially:
“Strategy”
“Execution”
“Scalability”

Scene 4 – Partners (14–19s):
Clean, premium background.
Title text appears:
“Partnered With”
Below the title, display logos side-by-side:
• Google logo
• Twitter logo
Logos appear with subtle fade or slide-in animation.
No distortion of brand logos.
Maintain official brand colors.

Scene 5 – Results & Benefits (19–25s):
B-roll: upward charts, smooth workflow animations, confident teams.
Motion graphics showing efficiency and growth.
On-screen text:
“Faster execution”
“Smarter workflows”
“Real results”

Scene 6 – Outro / Brand Close (25–30s):
Inovio Tech logo or brand name centered.
Soft reveal or glow animation.
Final text:
“Inovio Tech”
“Building the future of digital solutions”

STYLE & VISUAL DIRECTION:
- Premium, modern tech aesthetic
- Clean typography and motion graphics
- Confident, minimal design
- Smooth transitions (no flashy effects)
- Consistent pacing

VOICE & AUDIO:
- Professional, confident voiceover
- Neutral accent
- Calm, authoritative tone
- Mid-paced delivery
- Background music: modern, subtle, inspiring (low volume)

VIDEO SETTINGS:
- Length: 30 seconds
- Aspect ratio: Landscape (16:9)
- Avatar-less (no on-screen speakers)
- Focus on B-roll, motion graphics, typography, and logos

IMPORTANT NOTES:
- Use official Google and Twitter logos only
- Do not alter logo colors or proportions
- Do not add extra dialogue or scenes
- Do not introduce any avatar or character
